\begin_layout Subsection
User characteristics
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The only kind of user of the system is the customer of the car sharing service.
 We give for granted that users have access to the Internet.
 Users can look for a car and reserve it both via the web and the mobile
 application.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Constraints
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Regulatory policies
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It's user responsibility to ensure that the use of the system complies with
 the local laws and policies.
 The system must ask the user for the permission to acquire, store and process
 personal data and web cookies.
 The system must offer to the user the possibility to delete all personal
 data.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Hardware limitations
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The system has to run under the following worst-case conditions:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Mobile applications:
\end_layout

